Interface DataGetters

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    InternalArray, InternalRow
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryArray, BinaryRow, CastedRow, ColumnarArray, ColumnarRow, DefaultValueRow, FlinkRowWrapper, GenericArray, GenericRow, HivePaimonArray, JoinedRow, KeyProjectedRow, LazyGenericRow, NestedRow, OffsetRow, PartialRow, PartitionSettedRow, ProjectedRow, SafeBinaryArray, SafeBinaryRow, SparkRow

public interface DataGetters
    Getters to get data.
